{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/2013022101/ipv6-config-on-linux","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"c83c4294-70e8-5483-893d-d3d17dc7c322","html":"<p>毎回 Linux での IPv6 設定方法を忘れて設定ファイルや起動スクリプトを見ることになるので、メモっておく^^;。</p>\n<h2 id=\"centos-の場合\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#centos-%E3%81%AE%E5%A0%B4%E5%90%88\" aria-label=\"centos の場合 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>CentOS の場合</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">/etc/sysconfig/network</code> に <code class=\"language-text\">NETWORKING_IPV6=yes</code> を追加。</p>\n<p>手動設定の場合、必要に応じて <code class=\"language-text\">IPV6_DEFAULTDEV</code>, <code class=\"language-text\">IPV6_DEFAULTGW</code> も追加。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">NETWORKING_IPV6</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"yes\"</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#IPV6_DEFAULTDEV=eth0</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#IPV6_DEFAULTGW=fe80::1</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">/etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-if名</code> に <code class=\"language-text\">IPV6INIT=yes</code> を追加。</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">IPV6_AUTOCONF</code> などは環境に応じて適当に。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\"><span class=\"token assign-left variable\">IPV6INIT</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"yes\"</span>\n<span class=\"token assign-left variable\">IPV6_AUTOCONF</span><span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token string\">\"yes\"</span>        <span class=\"token comment\"># RA で自動設定</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#DHCPV6C=\"yes\"             # DHCPv6 で自動設定</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#IPV6ADDR=\"2001:db8::123\"  # 手動設定</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"ubuntu-の場合\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#ubuntu-%E3%81%AE%E5%A0%B4%E5%90%88\" aria-label=\"ubuntu の場合 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Ubuntu の場合</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">/etc/network/interfaces</code> に IPv6 用の設定を追加。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"shell\"><pre class=\"language-shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">auto eth0\niface eth0 inet6 auto      <span class=\"token comment\"># RA で自動設定</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#iface eth0 inet6 dhcp     # DHCPv6 で自動設定</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#iface eth0 inet6 static   # 手動設定</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#  address 2001:db8::123</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">#  netmask 64</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">## gateway 2001:db8::1</span></code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/2013022101/ipv6-config-on-linux","tagSlugs":["/tag/ubuntu/","/tag/cent-os/","/tag/network/"]},"frontmatter":{"date":"2013-02-21T05:07:08.000Z","description":"毎回 Linux での IPv6 設定方法を忘れて設定ファイルや起動スクリプトを見ることになるので、メモっておく^^;。","tags":["Ubuntu","CentOS","network"],"title":"Linux で IPv6 設定","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/2013022101/ipv6-config-on-linux"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","401334301","825871152"]}